  "title": "Pizza Maker (Italian Cuisine Restaurant Café) | Clementi | Gross up to $4,000",
  "description": "<p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Clementi Road, Singapore (JK Village)<br>\n💰 <strong>Salary:</strong> Gross up to $4,000 + OT pay<br>\n🕒 <strong>Working Hours:</strong> 6 days per week (Split Shifts: 10:00 AM – 2:00 PM &amp; 5:30 PM – 9:30 PM), 44 hours/week<br>\n📆 <strong>Rest Day:</strong> 1 day per week</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>About the Role</strong></p>\n<p>An established Italian cuisine restaurant café is seeking an experienced <strong>Pizza Maker</strong> to join its team. The ideal candidate should be skilled in authentic Italian-style pizza making, with a passion for quality, consistency, and teamwork.</p>\n<h3><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare and bake authentic Italian-style pizzas (not American style).</li>\n  <li>Ensure consistency, taste, and presentation of pizzas.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene in the pizza station.</li>\n  <li>Support kitchen operations and work collaboratively with the team.</li>\n  <li>Demonstrate professionalism, punctuality, and teamwork.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of proven experience as a Pizza Maker (Italian style).</li>\n  <li>Able to commit to <strong>6 working days/week (split shifts)</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Non-smoker and non-drinker preferred.</li>\n  <li>Clean, punctual, detail-oriented, and committed to long-term employment.</li>\n  <li>Open to <strong>Singaporeans and SPR only</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>What’s Offered</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Gross up to $4,000</li>\n  <li>Overtime pay (for hours beyond 44/week)</li>\n  <li>Training provided</li>\n  <li>2 meals per day</li>\n  <li>Uniform provided</li>\n</ul>\n<p>EA License No: 23C1703</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R1762582</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Wong Choo Sian, Jabez</p>",
